{"tid":1960083,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"英倫銀行指不會印錢助英國政府大幅增加開支","createTime":"2020-04-06T02:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T03:40:43.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"88fd6897148902db88a5b0f9558909d12e518a5b","tid":1960083,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:00:05.000Z","msg":"英倫銀行指不會印錢助英國政府大幅增加開支<br />\n06.04.2020 09:50<br />\n<br />\n英倫銀行行長貝利在金融時報撰文，強調不會「印錢」協助英國政府大幅增加開支，以應對疫情對經濟的衝擊。貝利指，債務貨幣化損害央行控制通脹的公信力，最終令央行的資產負債表不能持續，難以獨立決策控制通脹，強調不容許任何因素威脅百分之2的通脹目標，即使早前擴大量化寬鬆規模，央行仍控制日後何時和如何減持國債。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278958&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278958%26csid%3D261_367&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=8302ad7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278958&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"cdb28f4bb994b11572729b31eccbdbc072cf7bdd","tid":1960083,"uid":7436,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"堅, 美國咁玩真係好危險"},{"pid":"304e421b571f8299e9c4dc8330d126407d3a100f","tid":1960083,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdb28f4bb994b11572729b31eccbdbc072cf7bdd","tid":1960083,"uid":7436,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"堅, 美國咁玩真係好危險"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:57:13.000Z","msg":"咁佢係一哥, 咁玩係因為夠硬姐?"},{"pid":"db22c7af30e0718ae90bb79336b32846fe185d82","tid":1960083,"uid":442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"304e421b571f8299e9c4dc8330d126407d3a100f","tid":1960083,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdb28f4bb994b11572729b31eccbdbc072cf7bdd","tid":1960083,"uid":7436,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"堅, 美國咁玩真係好危險"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04